## Summary of Observations

### Positive observations
- Most students completed the assigned tasks without assistance.
- The Find Groups feature was the most useful function.
- Students liked the simple interface and navigation.
- Registration and Login pages were easy to understand.

### Common confusion points
- Search by course code.
- Search filter options.
- Join Group confirmation.
- Create Group form (optional fields).

### Overall conclusion

The Smart Study Group Finder MVP was successfully validated. Most users completed the required tasks and provided positive feedback. Minor improvements are recommended for the search functionality, Create Group form, Join Group workflow, and Notifications before the final implementation.
